blog.title: Here Be Voodoo
blog.description:
Tumblr of the webcomics: Here be Voodo
Here will be zombis, cute voodoo dolls with big knife, nudist werewolves and a ten years old with serious moral issues.
English main site: http://herebevoodoo.com
French main site:
http://icivontlesmorts.fr

title: Tumblr’s porn inquisition
body:
So. many of you now know about tumblr’s latest WTF.

I just did a quick check of the Here be Voodoo archive here and about one page on three are being flagged.

Now, I’m not surprised, Here be Voodoo IS Not Safe For Work because WHO  THE HELL READ A COMIC ABOUT ZOMBIE AND VOODOO DOLL AT WORK?!!! (also, I swear like a sailor, does tumblr know there is more than a way to be NSFW?)

That being said, I haven’t check all the way out, but I’ll bet you the parts that doesn’t pass the Tiities test doesn’t even have a titties on board and those who does will stay online. (Well, Ulf is not female, but he is dicking out on some pages and I’m curious to see if the Tumblinquisition is going to flag his sausage)

SO, I’ll let the last programmed pages go on time and then close this tumblr. I don’t want to fight with tumblr about if horror comics is better or worse than lady tits out (personal opinion, TITS OUT > ZOMBIE FLESH).

If you want to keep reading the comic, I invite you to go over the official website

http://herebevoodoo.com

Where you can comment, subscribe to the rss or by mail and follow a new pages every monday.

There is also the mirror site

http://herebevoodoo.smackjeeves.com

Or else the official facebook page (which is bilingual)

https://www.facebook.com/IciVontLesMorts

Congratulation Tumblr, you managed to fuck things up even worse that before. That must be an achievement.
